Click on Price List

        > Select the Department where you want to edit prices

        > Select an item from the List 



        > EDIT the price(s)
        
                       Note: At the Pharmacy, 
                       If you tick "Use Mark Up", the system will over write  the Selling Price with the Calculated Mark Up Price.
                       If you want to enter your own Selling Price, then untick the checkbox for "Use Mark Up".

        > Save
